{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"76974e344e","title":"“党是否能领导科学？”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"86ffb8db87","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"76974e344e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3e02d60f56","name":"白孝先"},{"id":"5d581a2dbc","name":"周茂成"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"8320407b5d","name":"沈启明"},{"id":"be5c925d21","name":"林墨荫"},{"id":"ce5df8948b","name":"龚振栋"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e4b817613d","type":"title","text":"“党是否能领导科学？”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"521b385d1e","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院林墨荫周茂成白孝先沈启明龚振栋","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"0eb61b3780","type":"paragraph","text":"林墨荫说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"912cf0667f","type":"paragraph","text":"「党是否能领导科学？为什么这么提？解放后党的领导有良心的人是不会反对的。但为什么提出党是否能领导，就是不学习就不能领导，这些老干部不懂科学，又不学习，就被群众丢在后面，就不能领导。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"733aee55d9","type":"paragraph","text":"周茂成说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"d6208dcbd5","type":"paragraph","text":"「党不能领导科学，没文化的怎能领导？」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"023e58bf91","type":"paragraph","text":"白孝先说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"e4d6dc4df9","type":"paragraph","text":"「美国科学有好多地方比苏联好，但没有党的领导。我们党团员看问题也应该科学、客观。」","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"d6ddb7144c","type":"paragraph","text":"沈启明说：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"631610417e","type":"paragraph","text":"「现在学生质量比解放前低，是因为党委会管得太多了，没有发挥老教授的作用。」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"76367d7a48","type":"paragraph","text":"龚振栋说：「我们的教育制度不如资本主义的教育制度，毕业后写不出什么东西来，也不如旧大学。」","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"385a199ab5","type":"paragraph","text":"姚鸿烈怀疑党能领导科学，他说：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"ae321ffbda","type":"paragraph","text":"「十二年赶上世界先进科学水平这不能，纸上写着容易，而实际上就难。」","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"b64ec39879","type":"paragraph","text":"李亚铃说：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"a50eb88fe2","type":"paragraph","text":"「五年了，干部学了多少？以前没条件学可以理解，可是到今天有些党委连普通知识还不知道，这些干部该打屁股，工作中接触到的干部，普通知识也很缺乏，怎能领导好科学呢？单靠马列主义不能领导科学。」","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"96b716fbf8","type":"paragraph","text":"孙增垣说：","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"85462d4cff","type":"paragraph","text":"「党员无才便是德，特别不能领导高等学校。」","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"c9e3f885ac","type":"paragraph","text":"何玉辉说：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"5e92653611","type":"paragraph","text":"「保密制度使人不能自由选择职业。」","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"e2000662cf","type":"paragraph","text":"「有些保密部门，成了独立王国，别的人都不能搞。这一方面取消了一部分人在这方面的劳动权，另一方面这种科学也未必发展得起来！」","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"e7fa4f0524","type":"paragraph","text":"「保密使某些科学部门成了一种只有某些人才能作的部门，防阻了交流，也排开了很多有才能的人，很难说真的发展得起来」。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"ca72d355ee","type":"paragraph","text":"「人事审查限制了很多有才能的人，几年以前科学院研究生的质量很低，科学院学部委员们很不满意，投票反对才通过了研究生的考试条例。」","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"b885b21dfb","type":"paragraph","text":"「陈以明没有经过人事审查听放射性探矿专家的课，而又让他搞放射性测井，这不是故意与人为难吗？」","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"d4c277814e","type":"paragraph","text":"龙国坤说：","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"},{"id":"42170a7e6e","type":"paragraph","text":"「现在的大学生质量低，不善于独立工作，学校没有一点学术气味」","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e"}],"page":{"id":"d9f588e569","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"76974e344e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}